1
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:01,340
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,410 --> 00:00:03,310
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,380 --> 00:00:05,140
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,240 --> 00:00:08,950
What kind of paintings
did Oh Jung Ran make off with?

5
00:00:09,410 --> 00:00:12,750
Chairman Park said they're paintings
that can't be reported stolen.

6
00:00:13,320 --> 00:00:16,150
They must be pieces that were traded
under the table to avoid taxes.

7
00:00:16,720 --> 00:00:18,390
Since Oh Jung Ran was
in charge of them,

8
00:00:18,820 --> 00:00:20,430
she'd know them better than anyone.

9
00:00:20,630 --> 00:00:21,630
But...

10
00:00:22,290 --> 00:00:25,130
If Oh Jung Ran disappears,
what happens with the divorce?

11
00:00:26,230 --> 00:00:29,000
Filing the divorce papers is useless
if she's not there in person.

12
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:31,140
Somehow, we have to get her
to come back.

13
00:00:48,020 --> 00:00:51,190
What on earth? Who drives like that?

14
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:54,590
Hey. Are you okay?

15
00:00:55,060 --> 00:00:58,530
- Yes, I'm fine. And you?
- I'm fine too.

16
00:01:00,630 --> 00:01:02,400
I thought it was Oh Jung Ran.

17
00:01:03,670 --> 00:01:04,670
Oh Jung Ran?

18
00:01:04,940 --> 00:01:08,140
Oh Jung Ran's cornered.
Who knows what she'll do?

19
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:11,480
It's unnerving that she stole
the paintings and then vanished.

20
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:15,710
I'm worried about what she might do
to you to protect her secrets.

21
00:01:33,330 --> 00:01:34,470
(Locked)

22
00:01:34,530 --> 00:01:35,530
(Unlocked)

23
00:01:57,290 --> 00:01:58,760
I'm glad it was you who came.

24
00:02:00,830 --> 00:02:03,830
At least you didn't trust that witch
Kim Myung Hui with everything.

25
00:02:07,970 --> 00:02:10,470
The passcode to this storage vault.

26
00:02:12,170 --> 00:02:13,540
You couldn't bring yourself
to give her that, right?

27
00:02:14,140 --> 00:02:15,140
What is this?

28
00:02:16,570 --> 00:02:19,910
You stole the paintings
and were just waiting for me?

29
00:02:21,010 --> 00:02:22,010
Why?

30
00:02:23,050 --> 00:02:24,080
To tell me you're sorry...

31
00:02:24,950 --> 00:02:27,050
and beg me to let it slide
this once?

32
00:02:29,050 --> 00:02:30,760
If I begged you for forgiveness,

33
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:33,760
would you even spare me?

34
00:02:34,330 --> 00:02:35,390
Good grief.

35
00:02:38,830 --> 00:02:42,070
How could I spare the person
who tried to kill my son?

36
00:02:42,570 --> 00:02:43,800
Not after you took advantage...

37
00:02:45,770 --> 00:02:49,640
of the precautions I put in place
at the warehouse.

38
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,480
Then tell me.

39
00:02:54,310 --> 00:02:55,710
Were you really going to kill me?

40
00:02:55,980 --> 00:02:56,980
I see.

41
00:02:57,680 --> 00:03:00,050
You figured it out,
which is why you pulled this stunt?

42
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:08,290
It's been 40 years
since we met at Munhwadang.

43
00:03:10,530 --> 00:03:12,430
We've been married
for over 30 years.

44
00:03:14,370 --> 00:03:15,400
But how could you...

45
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:17,770
even think of killing me?

46
00:03:19,570 --> 00:03:21,370
If our Hyun Jun finds out the truth,

47
00:03:21,870 --> 00:03:22,970
what are you going to do?

48
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:26,440
Your past as a murderer
has come to light,

49
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:30,250
along with your crime
of trying to harm my son!

50
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:35,920
Instead of prison,

51
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:39,660
you've chosen to go to your grave.

52
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:46,200
I'll take care of everything...

53
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:48,600
so Hyun Jun won't get hurt.

54
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,040
You don't have to worry
about a thing.

55
00:03:53,340 --> 00:03:55,410
All right? Don't worry.

56
00:03:56,310 --> 00:03:57,680
Don't you worry.

57
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,880
Don't worry.

58
00:04:07,050 --> 00:04:08,220
(Adele)

59
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,380
(Adele)

60
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:46,620
(Adele)

61
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:52,260
Oh Jung Ran...

62
00:04:54,970 --> 00:04:55,970
I at least...

63
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,470
gave you a chance, you know.

64
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:03,070
If you had said you'd spare me
for Hyun Jun's sake,

65
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:07,150
I wouldn't have betrayed you
like this.

66
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:13,050
The drug's hitting you hard,
isn't it?

67
00:05:13,890 --> 00:05:15,250
I never thought I'd end up...

68
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:19,020
using what I learned from you
against you.

69
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:23,760
You... How dare you...

70
00:05:23,930 --> 00:05:26,100
You're the one
who made me like this!

71
00:05:31,940 --> 00:05:33,000
Jung Ran?

72
00:05:45,850 --> 00:05:47,620
I've taken care of Director Kang.

73
00:05:53,390 --> 00:05:54,390
From now on,

74
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,230
I'll be the one
painting the picture.

75
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,330
A new one, in a world
without Park Tae Ho.

76
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:06,700
But don't you worry.

77
00:06:07,910 --> 00:06:08,910
For now,

78
00:06:10,410 --> 00:06:12,910
you're more useful to me alive
than dead.

79
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:25,190
Ms. Kim.

80
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,190
Is something wrong?

81
00:06:27,530 --> 00:06:30,630
The chairman hasn't come home yet.

82
00:06:31,060 --> 00:06:33,830
He said he had work at the gallery.
I guess he's just running late.

83
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:37,170
It's just that
I can't reach Director Kang either.

84
00:06:37,670 --> 00:06:40,640
He always calls ahead whenever
the chairman is running late.

85
00:06:41,110 --> 00:06:45,210
With the house in an uproar
over Ms. Oh, I'm very worried.

86
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:49,050
I know what Ms. Oh is capable of,

87
00:06:49,710 --> 00:06:52,980
so I'm worried something
might have happened to him.

88
00:06:53,250 --> 00:06:56,590
Wait.
I'll try calling the gallery again.

89
00:06:57,390 --> 00:07:00,530
No. Check on Min Jun first.

90
00:07:01,860 --> 00:07:03,630
Right, I'll do that.

91
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,580
Ta-da.

92
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:31,460
Remember when you got rid
of our burned watches?

93
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:33,720
I promised I'd make you a new set.

94
00:07:34,230 --> 00:07:35,230
What do you think?

95
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:42,030
What is it? Don't you like it?

96
00:07:43,730 --> 00:07:45,040
No, it's not that.

97
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:49,310
Then what is it?
You've been quiet all evening.

98
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:53,980
- Hyun Jun said...
- Park Hyun Jun?

99
00:07:55,710 --> 00:07:56,980
What did he say?

100
00:07:58,780 --> 00:08:03,050
Forget that. You were out of line
at the cafe earlier.

101
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,320
With what?

102
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,760
You can't be serious.
With that waitress?

103
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:14,770
You expected me to just stand there
while she was making eyes at you?

104
00:08:19,540 --> 00:08:21,070
All right, I get it.

105
00:08:21,970 --> 00:08:25,080
I'll say I was in the wrong.
Just don't be mad.

106
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:29,110
When you look at me
with those cold eyes,

107
00:08:29,650 --> 00:08:31,580
it honestly scares me.

108
00:08:32,220 --> 00:08:33,220
It scares you?

109
00:08:37,020 --> 00:08:39,020
As much as I love you,

110
00:08:39,590 --> 00:08:40,660
I'm just as afraid.

111
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:44,260
It scares me when you're cold to me.

112
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:47,130
I'm always worried...

113
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:49,130
that you'll grow to hate me.

114
00:08:51,770 --> 00:08:53,940
From the moment we met until now,

115
00:08:54,610 --> 00:08:57,040
I've always been more in love
than you.

116
00:08:58,140 --> 00:09:01,180
I rushed to come back to work
just so I could be with you,

117
00:09:02,110 --> 00:09:04,750
and I get jealous
of some random server.

118
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,850
That's how much I need you.

119
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:10,760
Before you get so angry,

120
00:09:11,460 --> 00:09:13,560
can't you try to see
where I'm coming from?

121
00:09:17,830 --> 00:09:19,230
Whatever else I may have forgotten,

122
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:22,130
I should've remembered
your feelings.

123
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:26,300
I feel like I've really forgotten
what's most important.

124
00:09:27,140 --> 00:09:28,140
I'm sorry.

125
00:09:29,510 --> 00:09:32,080
Give me your hand.
Let me put yours on first.

126
00:09:39,220 --> 00:09:42,620
I wish you would never
get your memory back.

127
00:09:43,220 --> 00:09:46,460
I wish you'd forget Jin Ju and Chloe
and just smile at me,

128
00:09:47,060 --> 00:09:49,060
and only me.

129
00:10:44,950 --> 00:10:46,180
You finally see me.

130
00:10:50,490 --> 00:10:52,060
Don't go by yourself.

131
00:10:52,690 --> 00:10:55,430
Like this. Let me join you.

132
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:03,400
- I get it, so please let go.
- Just for today.

133
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,910
Let me have this.

134
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:13,640
What's going on with my father
is crushing me,

135
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:17,420
and my mom, who's always hitting
rock bottom, is too much to handle.

136
00:11:19,650 --> 00:11:22,050
Holding on to you like this
is the only way...

137
00:11:23,990 --> 00:11:25,620
I think I can survive.

138
00:11:28,660 --> 00:11:30,690
The person
who's hurting you the most...

139
00:11:36,470 --> 00:11:37,700
might...

140
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,470
be me.

141
00:11:39,470 --> 00:11:40,870
If this is about Min Jun,

142
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:44,340
don't.

143
00:11:46,810 --> 00:11:48,080
Even though I know...

144
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:51,080
how much you're struggling,

145
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:53,920
I still...

146
00:11:58,820 --> 00:12:00,960
I need you
to help me convince Chairman Park.

147
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:05,530
I also want to meet board members
who were close to your mother.

148
00:12:06,130 --> 00:12:07,730
If President Kim Myung Hui...

149
00:12:07,730 --> 00:12:10,330
takes your mother's place
as the chairman's wife,

150
00:12:11,070 --> 00:12:13,540
it could get in the way
of our plans.

151
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:17,510
That's...

152
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:21,810
the kind of thing
I want to talk about.

153
00:12:26,580 --> 00:12:29,850
It'll be hard to talk to my father
because of what's going on with Mom,

154
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:32,720
but I'll arrange a meeting
with the board.

155
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:34,360
And as for President Kim,

156
00:12:35,930 --> 00:12:37,260
Min Jun's mother...

157
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:41,470
She'll take Min Jun's side.

158
00:12:42,630 --> 00:12:43,670
Is that...

159
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:47,140
the answer you wanted?

160
00:12:51,540 --> 00:12:52,540
I'm sorry.

161
00:12:57,620 --> 00:12:58,780
But at least...

162
00:12:59,980 --> 00:13:01,750
you get how I feel.

163
00:13:03,220 --> 00:13:04,760
Meanwhile, my parents...

164
00:13:05,990 --> 00:13:08,630
don't even care how I feel.

165
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:12,400
But you hold my hand like this,

166
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:15,500
and you even tell me you're sorry.

167
00:13:17,900 --> 00:13:18,970
So...

168
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:22,410
don't be the person
who's hurting me the most.

169
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:27,140
Be the one who comforts me.

170
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,820
Be that person for me.

171
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:51,740
Min Jun, are you okay?
Nothing happened, right?

172
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:52,800
I'm fine.

173
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:55,070
I just didn't see the text asking me
to come home early until later.

174
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,440
Did something happen
at the house again?

175
00:13:58,740 --> 00:14:00,910
It's about the chairman.

176
00:14:04,820 --> 00:14:05,880
Well,

177
00:14:06,550 --> 00:14:08,990
it looks like there's a problem
at the gallery.

178
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:11,760
I tried to check
the chairman's access logs,

179
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:14,760
but the CCTV and security system
were off.

180
00:14:14,890 --> 00:14:17,930
You're saying you don't know
the chairman's whereabouts?

181
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:22,970
Currently, Manager Kang
and the chairman are missing.

182
00:14:23,470 --> 00:14:24,600
No one's been able to reach him...

183
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:26,500
ever since he went to the gallery
because of Ms. Oh.

184
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:29,910
Do you think
she could be behind this?

185
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:58,340
Oh Jung Ran...

186
00:14:59,700 --> 00:15:03,040
Oh Jung Ran, untie me right now!

187
00:15:10,050 --> 00:15:11,950
You still don't get it, do you?

188
00:15:15,020 --> 00:15:18,020
Did you expect me
to tremble in fear and untie you...

189
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:20,090
just because you yelled?

190
00:15:20,590 --> 00:15:22,030
Oh Jung Ran!

191
00:15:25,830 --> 00:15:26,830
Then again,

192
00:15:27,400 --> 00:15:29,770
I guess that's how I lived
beside you.

193
00:15:31,570 --> 00:15:35,340
Terrified of you, always walking
on eggshells, trembling,

194
00:15:35,570 --> 00:15:40,110
desperately trying to get
on your good side,

195
00:15:41,710 --> 00:15:43,910
only to be hurt and disappointed
every single time.

196
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:47,750
That's how it's been
for over 30 years.

197
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:52,860
I don't know
why I put up with it for so long.

198
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:55,360
If you stop this right now,

199
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:00,460
I'll forgive you.

200
00:16:00,660 --> 00:16:02,000
Just untie me already.

201
00:16:02,530 --> 00:16:03,570
You'll forgive me?

202
00:16:04,700 --> 00:16:07,140
I'm the one who should be
doing the forgiving, not you.

203
00:16:07,710 --> 00:16:09,810
You tried to choke me to death.

204
00:16:10,010 --> 00:16:11,010
Fine.

205
00:16:11,610 --> 00:16:12,680
Fine, I get it.

206
00:16:14,450 --> 00:16:18,280
I was wrong, so just untie me.

207
00:16:18,780 --> 00:16:23,390
Let's go back together, make up,
and put this all behind us.

208
00:16:29,930 --> 00:16:30,930
Go back?

209
00:16:32,300 --> 00:16:35,030
To a life spent competing over
who's better?

210
00:16:36,470 --> 00:16:38,300
I'm sick of walking on eggshells
around you,

211
00:16:38,300 --> 00:16:40,100
and now I have to do it
around Kim Myung Hui too?

212
00:16:41,970 --> 00:16:42,970
I...

213
00:16:43,510 --> 00:16:44,880
refuse to live like that anymore.

214
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:47,780
I told you, didn't I?

215
00:16:48,880 --> 00:16:50,950
I'm painting a new picture.

216
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:56,750
You just lie there
with your eyes closed...

217
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:58,920
and watch the show.

218
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:07,400
No!

219
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:11,100
Oh Jung Ran!

220
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:16,510
There's been no word all night.
Something must have happened.

221
00:17:17,010 --> 00:17:19,510
We need to call the police
right now.

222
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,480
No, not the police.

223
00:17:22,250 --> 00:17:24,680
It would cause a panic
at Adele Group.

224
00:17:25,850 --> 00:17:27,850
For starters,
the stock price would nosedive.

225
00:17:28,390 --> 00:17:29,390
Mother.

226
00:17:30,750 --> 00:17:32,660
Now that my father isn't here,

227
00:17:33,990 --> 00:17:35,460
you're starting to sound
just like him.

228
00:17:37,360 --> 00:17:39,160
It's what's best
for your mother, too.

229
00:17:39,630 --> 00:17:43,570
If the police investigate,
everyone will know she was disowned,

230
00:17:43,700 --> 00:17:46,800
making her the prime suspect
in the chairman's kidnapping.

231
00:17:54,710 --> 00:17:56,480
Oh Jung Ran kidnapped Chairman Park?

232
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:58,250
That's what Hyun Jun said.

233
00:17:58,350 --> 00:18:00,580
Apparently, that's what
President Kim suspects.

234
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:01,990
Why would Oh Jung Ran do that?

235
00:18:02,650 --> 00:18:04,020
Because she got kicked out
of the family?

236
00:18:04,760 --> 00:18:07,990
But would she really go that far?

237
00:18:08,490 --> 00:18:11,500
There must be more to it, right?

238
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:16,300
So, what are you going to do?

239
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:19,370
- Secretary Jung.
- Yes, ma'am.

240
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:23,040
Hire some people you can trust
to be discreet,

241
00:18:23,270 --> 00:18:26,580
and have them look
for Manager Kang, the chairman,

242
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:28,450
as well as Oh Jung Ran.

243
00:18:28,550 --> 00:18:29,950
Understood.

244
00:18:30,710 --> 00:18:32,050
What should I tell the company?

245
00:18:32,850 --> 00:18:36,550
Tell them he's recovering
for health reasons.

246
00:18:37,290 --> 00:18:38,990
It's nothing serious,

247
00:18:39,590 --> 00:18:41,830
but he'll be stepping back
from management.

248
00:18:43,860 --> 00:18:45,300
Stepping away from management?

249
00:18:48,070 --> 00:18:51,340
He's only been gone for one night.
You're jumping the gun.

250
00:18:52,300 --> 00:18:54,040
Let's just say he's on vacation
or a business trip.

251
00:18:55,270 --> 00:18:58,280
I'd hate to think
you're making a power grab...

252
00:18:59,310 --> 00:19:00,680
while my father's away.

253
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:09,250
I know this is a new situation,
and it's unsettling for all of us.

254
00:19:09,890 --> 00:19:11,050
Myself included.

255
00:19:11,390 --> 00:19:13,660
I hope the chairman returns soon,

256
00:19:14,390 --> 00:19:16,630
but we have to be prepared
for the worst.

257
00:19:17,430 --> 00:19:20,260
Things are going to get busy
for you two,

258
00:19:20,730 --> 00:19:24,200
so for the time being,
I need you to do exactly as I say.

259
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:31,240
Sure.
But please, find our father quickly.

260
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:34,980
Of course. Absolutely.

261
00:19:49,930 --> 00:19:51,930
Do you really think
Oh Jung Ran is behind this?

262
00:19:52,930 --> 00:19:55,000
If she didn't want the divorce,
she could've just disappeared.

263
00:19:55,830 --> 00:19:59,670
If her secret was the problem,
why target the chairman and not you?

264
00:19:59,900 --> 00:20:00,900
What if...

265
00:20:01,570 --> 00:20:04,310
Chairman Park targeted Oh Jung Ran
because of what she did to Min Jun,

266
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:07,710
and Oh Jung Ran just struck first?

267
00:20:07,980 --> 00:20:08,980
What?

268
00:20:09,780 --> 00:20:12,480
You think this is the result of them
trying to kill each other?

269
00:20:12,950 --> 00:20:17,190
For now, I'm just considering
the worst-case scenario.

270
00:20:17,490 --> 00:20:20,920
It's hard to imagine Oh Jung Ran
getting the better of Chairman Park.

271
00:20:21,730 --> 00:20:23,160
But even if that were the case,

272
00:20:23,830 --> 00:20:25,830
why should we be worried about him?

273
00:20:26,830 --> 00:20:30,530
After everything he did to Dr. Baek,
who cares what happens to him?

274
00:20:31,540 --> 00:20:33,070
This isn't for Chairman Park's sake.

275
00:20:33,600 --> 00:20:36,210
I'm trying to find him
because I can't trust Oh Jung Ran.

276
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:40,740
If Oh Jung Ran
is really behind this,

277
00:20:41,110 --> 00:20:43,950
then there's no telling
what she'll do next.

278
00:20:44,980 --> 00:20:47,950
In any case,
Oh Jung Ran is the problem.

279
00:20:48,220 --> 00:20:50,050
So while we're looking
for Oh Jung Ran,

280
00:20:50,550 --> 00:20:53,460
we're going to make the most
of Chairman Park's absence.

281
00:20:54,460 --> 00:20:55,560
Make the most of it?

282
00:20:58,860 --> 00:21:02,230
While the chairman is gone,
we need to build our power base.

283
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:04,370
I'll consolidate
the Executive Office,

284
00:21:04,370 --> 00:21:05,670
Finance, and Legal divisions...

285
00:21:06,070 --> 00:21:07,740
and bring
all of the company's information,

286
00:21:08,170 --> 00:21:09,970
assets, and legal affairs
under my control.

287
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:13,080
Can you really pull all that off
at once?

288
00:21:13,610 --> 00:21:15,080
I have a plan.

289
00:21:15,380 --> 00:21:17,380
Call a meeting
with the executives immediately.

290
00:21:18,180 --> 00:21:19,180
Sure.

291
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:23,320
(Adele)

292
00:21:40,500 --> 00:21:42,840
I assume you've all heard
about the Chairman.

293
00:21:43,740 --> 00:21:44,740
Yes.

294
00:21:45,580 --> 00:21:48,410
Is he going to be all right?

295
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:52,780
Do we have any idea
how long he'll be gone?

296
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:56,050
It's hard to say at this point.

297
00:21:58,990 --> 00:22:01,360
What about his wife, then?

298
00:22:01,760 --> 00:22:03,130
We haven't been able
to reach her either.

299
00:22:03,630 --> 00:22:04,730
Is something wrong?

300
00:22:05,930 --> 00:22:07,660
She'll also be away for a while.

301
00:22:07,660 --> 00:22:10,970
Actually, she's gone for good.

302
00:22:11,740 --> 00:22:12,900
For good?

303
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:14,640
Secretary Jung.

304
00:22:14,940 --> 00:22:15,940
Yes, ma'am.

305
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:23,510
(Application for Divorce
by Mutual Consent)

306
00:22:30,120 --> 00:22:33,320
The chairman is in the process
of divorcing his wife.

307
00:22:35,560 --> 00:22:37,730
What? Is this true?

308
00:22:38,230 --> 00:22:39,230
Wait a minute.

309
00:22:40,230 --> 00:22:42,670
Couldn't these papers be forged?

310
00:22:43,600 --> 00:22:46,140
If this turns out
to be untrue later on,

311
00:22:47,040 --> 00:22:48,270
you can hold me accountable.

312
00:22:48,570 --> 00:22:51,170
So, you're saying
the divorce is real?

313
00:22:51,940 --> 00:22:52,940
But why?

314
00:22:53,780 --> 00:22:55,950
The reason for their divorce
is a private matter,

315
00:22:56,550 --> 00:22:58,250
so I will not comment further.

316
00:22:59,580 --> 00:23:01,620
Until the chairman returns,

317
00:23:02,150 --> 00:23:04,050
we must focus on
keeping the company stable.

318
00:23:04,990 --> 00:23:05,990
For that reason,

319
00:23:06,820 --> 00:23:10,160
I am forming
an Emergency Management Team.

320
00:23:11,060 --> 00:23:12,160
- An Emergency Management Team?
- What?

321
00:23:12,330 --> 00:23:13,860
What's an Emergency Management Team?

322
00:23:14,500 --> 00:23:15,500
What the...

323
00:23:17,730 --> 00:23:18,740
Wait, but...

324
00:23:21,570 --> 00:23:22,870
Adele Group...

325
00:23:23,910 --> 00:23:26,080
is now under emergency management?

326
00:23:28,550 --> 00:23:32,180
Why would Oh Jung Ran
kidnap Park Tae Ho?

327
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:36,320
The question is,
what is she planning to do next?

328
00:23:38,520 --> 00:23:42,430
President Kim Myung Hui seems
to be overlooking that.

329
00:23:43,130 --> 00:23:44,230
We need to move quickly...

330
00:23:45,030 --> 00:23:47,530
and track down
Oh Jung Ran ourselves.

331
00:23:53,340 --> 00:23:55,140
Okay, got it.

332
00:23:57,210 --> 00:23:58,410
They still haven't found...

333
00:23:58,410 --> 00:24:00,810
Chairman Park and Oh Jung Ran,
have they?

334
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:05,020
They're the best,
so let's give them some more time.

335
00:24:06,580 --> 00:24:07,580
Okay.

336
00:24:08,950 --> 00:24:11,390
So, what's your plan now?

337
00:24:12,320 --> 00:24:14,320
You were trying to strip
Chairman Park of his power,

338
00:24:14,860 --> 00:24:16,390
but it looks like Kim Myung Hui...

339
00:24:16,390 --> 00:24:17,930
and Park Min Jun
will end up with it instead.

340
00:24:18,860 --> 00:24:22,670
Regardless, I'll still make my move
to take over Adele.

341
00:24:24,270 --> 00:24:27,340
I can't let someone else be the one
to punish Chairman Park.

342
00:24:28,870 --> 00:24:33,080
James, have the team keep looking
for Chairman Park and Oh Jung Ran.

343
00:24:33,780 --> 00:24:36,250
I'm going to Adele
to see what's going on.

344
00:24:37,380 --> 00:24:38,880
All right, let's get moving.

345
00:24:40,820 --> 00:24:42,650
- What is this?
- What's going on?

346
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:47,920
What happened?
Where on earth did he go?

347
00:24:50,860 --> 00:24:51,860
What the...

348
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:56,230
What's going on?
Why is everyone in a panic?

349
00:24:58,270 --> 00:25:00,170
- Did you hear?
- I did.

350
00:25:17,520 --> 00:25:19,490
Don't you think you're coming here
a little too often?

351
00:25:20,660 --> 00:25:22,660
You're not even married
to Park Hyun Jun yet.

352
00:25:24,030 --> 00:25:25,560
Know your place.

353
00:25:27,060 --> 00:25:28,770
The same goes for you, doesn't it?

354
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:32,800
I heard you got kicked out
of the company.

355
00:25:34,840 --> 00:25:39,480
I'm helping Director Park Min Jun
with company business.

356
00:25:42,110 --> 00:25:45,650
I'm here on my father's behalf
to assess the situation at Adele.

357
00:25:47,180 --> 00:25:49,920
With our exclusive development
rights project coming up,

358
00:25:50,350 --> 00:25:53,960
it's only right to check on things
now that the chairman is away.

359
00:25:55,760 --> 00:25:57,290
Exclusive development rights?

360
00:25:58,430 --> 00:26:02,200
Wait, forget that.
The chairman is away?

361
00:26:02,600 --> 00:26:05,500
- Why?
- For someone helping Mr. Park,

362
00:26:06,400 --> 00:26:07,670
you're a little behind on the news.

363
00:26:14,810 --> 00:26:16,150
Park Min Jun!

364
00:26:19,050 --> 00:26:22,320
Min Jun, I heard the chairman
has gone missing. What's going on?

365
00:26:23,050 --> 00:26:24,290
I don't really know myself.

366
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:27,460
They're saying Hyun Jun's mother
kidnapped my father.

367
00:26:28,390 --> 00:26:30,930
What? Ms. Oh kidnapped the chairman?

368
00:26:32,230 --> 00:26:35,570
You've always been by my side,
so you know about my family, right?

369
00:26:36,270 --> 00:26:38,000
- What?
- I've been confused...

370
00:26:38,100 --> 00:26:40,070
ever since my accident.

371
00:26:40,500 --> 00:26:43,910
Why would Hyun Jun's mother
try to kill me?

372
00:26:44,770 --> 00:26:46,140
Just start by telling me that.

373
00:26:50,450 --> 00:26:52,420
That's not
what's important right now.

374
00:26:52,780 --> 00:26:56,290
Your mother's forming an Emergency
Management Team. You must help her.

375
00:26:57,350 --> 00:26:59,720
With the chairman and Ms. Oh
both out of the picture,

376
00:27:00,360 --> 00:27:02,830
your mother
will take over management,

377
00:27:03,360 --> 00:27:06,060
and you'll become the successor
instead of Park Hyun Jun.

378
00:27:06,860 --> 00:27:09,300
Did you talk to your mom
about getting me reinstated?

379
00:27:09,900 --> 00:27:12,240
I think I could be a valuable asset
to the Emergency Management Team.

380
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:15,340
I'll go see if there's
anything I can do to help.

381
00:27:22,510 --> 00:27:25,020
Is she still avoiding
talking about my accident?

382
00:27:25,780 --> 00:27:27,320
My mother and Choi Yu Na.

383
00:27:27,320 --> 00:27:28,850
Why are they hiding this from me?

384
00:27:30,190 --> 00:27:32,420
What exactly happened...

385
00:27:33,390 --> 00:27:35,190
during the time I can't remember?

386
00:27:47,100 --> 00:27:48,570
Kim Myung Hui and Park Min Jun.

387
00:27:49,270 --> 00:27:51,510
Look at them,
living as if nothing's changed.

388
00:27:52,910 --> 00:27:54,580
Even after
I was thrown out like this,

389
00:27:55,180 --> 00:27:56,450
they act like nothing's happened.

390
00:27:57,480 --> 00:28:01,050
Those two must be relieved
that you're gone.

391
00:28:02,050 --> 00:28:04,390
Why did you have someone follow them
and take pictures?

392
00:28:06,190 --> 00:28:09,260
I was hoping
they'd look out for Hyun Jun.

393
00:28:09,590 --> 00:28:11,530
I checked the photos myself.

394
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:15,600
It seems that Chloe
is taking care of Hyun Jun.

395
00:28:19,870 --> 00:28:21,810
Am I supposed to be relieved?

396
00:28:25,340 --> 00:28:26,740
So what are you going to do now?

397
00:28:40,960 --> 00:28:41,960
Manager Kang.

398
00:28:44,060 --> 00:28:45,300
Are you still thinking about it?

399
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:51,030
I know you're Park Tae Ho's man,

400
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:54,500
but he's just going
to keep lying there in that bed.

401
00:28:57,070 --> 00:29:00,410
Are you okay with your mother's
medical support being cut off?

402
00:29:02,050 --> 00:29:03,050
Ms. Oh!

403
00:29:03,310 --> 00:29:06,680
You have no other choice,
so why pretend you're deciding?

404
00:29:07,950 --> 00:29:09,820
Don't you know
the sooner you decide, the better?

405
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:17,190
I'll do it. I'll do as you say.

406
00:29:26,770 --> 00:29:30,110
Are you trying to interfere
with emergency management?

407
00:29:32,140 --> 00:29:35,310
As I see it, Chloe is an outsider
with no authority here.

408
00:29:36,210 --> 00:29:37,310
Being my fiancee...

409
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:39,950
gives her every right.

410
00:29:39,950 --> 00:29:42,050
Did the chairman approve
of your marriage?

411
00:29:42,250 --> 00:29:43,250
Does it matter?

412
00:29:43,590 --> 00:29:46,520
Now that my father is gone,
I don't think his approval matters.

413
00:29:47,320 --> 00:29:49,690
I'll be moving forward
with the marriage...

414
00:29:50,530 --> 00:29:51,530
and the exclusive
development rights.

415
00:29:52,460 --> 00:29:54,230
You can do as you please
with the marriage,

416
00:29:54,760 --> 00:29:58,370
but the exclusive development rights
require the CEO's approval.

417
00:29:58,700 --> 00:30:00,770
Now that you've seized
emergency control of the company,

418
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:03,070
are you saying you won't approve it?

419
00:30:04,140 --> 00:30:08,580
Does that mean you're opposed
to the exclusive development rights?

420
00:30:09,610 --> 00:30:10,710
That goes without saying,
doesn't it?

421
00:30:15,450 --> 00:30:16,720
During a crisis,

422
00:30:17,150 --> 00:30:19,760
we can't approve a deal
that's this one-sided.

423
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:21,560
Hey.

424
00:30:22,990 --> 00:30:24,390
This has nothing to do with you.

425
00:30:24,690 --> 00:30:27,730
I'm here on Min Jun's behalf.

426
00:30:28,400 --> 00:30:31,070
You're trying to take
Min Jun's place as the successor,

427
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,400
and I'm here to stop you.

428
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:37,210
Everyone has said their piece.
You may leave now.

429
00:30:51,150 --> 00:30:52,760
Congratulations, Mother.

430
00:30:53,490 --> 00:30:54,490
Congratulations?

431
00:30:54,520 --> 00:30:56,860
For seizing control of Adele.

432
00:30:58,900 --> 00:31:01,930
Even so, now isn't exactly
the right time for congratulations.

433
00:31:03,270 --> 00:31:06,640
Anyway, you're going to make Min Jun
the successor now, aren't you?

434
00:31:07,700 --> 00:31:10,640
But Min Jun still hasn't
recovered his memory,

435
00:31:11,440 --> 00:31:14,580
so if you reinstate me,
I'll stay by his side and help him.

436
00:31:15,950 --> 00:31:18,210
I'll think about it. You may go now.

437
00:31:18,950 --> 00:31:20,020
I have a lot to do.

438
00:31:22,690 --> 00:31:23,690
Sure.

439
00:31:35,060 --> 00:31:36,100
Park Hyun Jun...

440
00:31:37,230 --> 00:31:39,240
He's more aggressive about
the succession than I expected.

441
00:31:40,570 --> 00:31:42,640
Is he getting ambitious
because of Chloe?

442
00:31:43,410 --> 00:31:47,040
Or is Chloe the one pushing him?

443
00:31:51,050 --> 00:31:53,320
(Mrs. Han)

444
00:32:06,700 --> 00:32:09,670
(Adele Group)

445
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:14,640
(Power of Delegation
for Acting Duties)

446
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:23,080
We have to stop Oh Jung Ran...

447
00:32:23,550 --> 00:32:25,650
before she returns
with the power of attorney.

448
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:53,440
(Pearl in Red)

449
00:32:53,540 --> 00:32:55,310
If Oh Jung Ran can't be stopped,

450
00:32:55,450 --> 00:32:57,610
the company
and Min Jun's place as successor...

451
00:32:57,610 --> 00:32:58,750
will both go down the drain.

452
00:32:59,180 --> 00:33:00,750
An emergency board meeting?

453
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:01,750
President Kim is trying...

454
00:33:01,750 --> 00:33:03,750
- Min Jun!
- to take control of the company.

455
00:33:03,920 --> 00:33:06,860
We must find your mother and prepare
before the board meeting.

456
00:33:07,190 --> 00:33:09,360
It's about time
we made our move, honey.

457
00:33:09,660 --> 00:33:12,200
Want to know why I spared your life?

458
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:13,700
You're about to find out.

459
00:33:14,230 --> 00:33:16,230
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
